# Environment Variables for LegalEase Backend

## Required Variables

### Server Configuration
PORT=4000
NODE_ENV=development
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
CLIENT_URLS=http://localhost:5173,https://your-production-frontend.vercel.app

### Database
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string

### Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

### AI Service (Groq - Free)
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

### Email (OTP delivery)
EMAIL_USER=your_gmail_address
EMAIL_PASS=your_gmail_app_password

## How to Get Your Groq API Key (FREE):
1. Visit: https://console.groq.com/keys
2. Sign up/login with Google or email (no credit card required)
3. Click "Create API Key"
4. Copy the key and paste it above
5. Restart your server

## Model Used
- Llama 3.3 70B Versatile (Ultra-fast, free inference)
